Trent: &quot;I think for 70-75 minutes we were outstanding - up there with one of our best performances - counter-pressing, taking the ball off them for fun, they couldn't really get out. Really top drawer from us. We were in the driving seat. Then the tables turned.&quot; #awlfc [lfc]<br />
<br />
&quot;Then they put the game to bed within a matter of 5-10 minutes and that is football. It happened so quickly - it just happened in a moment and we've just crumbled at the end of the day.&quot;

